Odette Laure https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odette_Laure 0 Odette Laure (28 February 1917 – 10 June 2004) was a French actress and cabaret singer. She appeared in 57 films and television shows between 1950 and 2001. She was nominated for the César Award for Best Supporting Actress for Daddy Nostalgia (1990). She was born Odette Yvonne Marie Dhommée in Paris, where she died. Odette_Laure ( 28_February_1917 – 10_June_2004 ) was a_French_actress_and_cabaret_singer .
